flowchart TD
    A[Candidate Run] --> C{Same Dataset Version?}
    B[Baseline Run] --> C
    C -- No --> X[Not Comparable]
    C -- Yes --> D{Same Metric Versions?}
    D -- No --> X
    D -- Yes --> E{Same Normalization Profile?}
    E -- No --> W[Comparable With Warnings]
    E -- Yes --> F{Same Sample Inclusion Rules?}
    F -- No --> X
    F -- Yes --> G{Same Hardware Profile?}
    G -- No --> W
    G -- Yes --> H[Strictly Comparable]
    H --> I[Statistical Comparison]
    W --> I
    I --> J[Regression Gate Decision]
